reviewText: Are one of my favorite type of films. The dubbing was not bad either, you can hardly tell. Also, the movie itself is digestable, and action packed. If your looking for something hard and obscure to find in the genre of cyber punk films, get this for your collection. Cool movie trailers in the beginning, and also the packaging was good too. Pretty much in solid almost mint condition. Thanks and bow to nostalgic webmaster glory! Than watch it again sometime soon to refresh your memory.
